txt.en: Through your efforts, the people of Upper Lebennin will no longer need to live in fear of mounted Haradrim raiders.\n\nYou have done a great service to the people of Gondor, and your efforts shall be remembered among the folk of these lands.

While patrolling the plains of Upper Lebennin, you have encountered the brutal Haradrim captain, Kasota, and his warband. The folk of Upper Lebennin have been harried and killed by the raiding Haradrim, and would be grateful to see such a dangerous foe gone from their lands.\n\nYou should defeat Kasota and his warband before he can bring any further harm to the people of Gondor.
Kasota and his warband can be found somewhere in the southern plains of Upper Lebennin.\n\nYou should defeat Kasota and his warband for the good of the people of Gondor.
